{"tid":2448013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家組：所有死亡個案及嚴重事件 均與接種疫苗沒有直接關係","createTime":"2021-03-15T15:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T15:17:01.000Z","uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75c9a88b9d1505b0a0d850f09b6a1c6d59a7c704","tid":2448013,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"專家委員會：七宗死亡個案均與疫苗沒直接關係<br />\n2021-03-15 HKT 22:55<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580742-20210315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580742-20210315.htm&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=bbc94e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580742-20210315.htm&h=839c8e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580742-20210315.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n本港再有一宗，即第7宗接種科興疫苗後不適，其後死亡個案，死者是一名63歲男子。專家委員會話，至今7宗死亡個案，均與接種疫苗沒有直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會初步認為，7宗曾經接種疫苗、之後死亡，以及幾宗嚴重異常事件，均與接種疫苗沒有直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n委員會表示，死亡個案都有心血管疾病或者其他器官問題，但仍須等待解剖報告，才能總結與接種疫苗的因果關係。"},{"pid":"a23671b3351c1429c1b34bc7590f5a1a261cbac1","tid":2448013,"uid":361751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"如何取你壽命 誰說一定 切勿責怪科興<br />\n明明生死算命數 基因生肖 或時辰注定<br />\n中風中得太早<br />\n繼續輪候 給眾人來助興<br />\n強國亦信係太醒 還是對它尊敬"},{"pid":"cb9901a8e1f78fd34981b703abfd43cc0d053b1f","tid":2448013,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"專家組開會開咗有無一分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用個腦諗下都知唔關科興事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eaef6ecce35130edd2c62a2abd7e1a758c18ae6","tid":2448013,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"呢位磚家打BIONTECH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"